title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: When attempting to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown. This issue occurs when the report includes a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
OB: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the table containing the highlight and map rules.
EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions when using the export feature on a table that includes highlight and map rules.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table that contains a group row with a highlight rule and a map rule.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table. Ensure that the export feature is enabled and functioning properly.
